@{
    ViewBag.Title = "充值";
    string channelId = ViewBag.ChannelId;
}
@section styles{
    @Styles.Render("~/Content/wxIndex")
}
<link href="~/Content/wx/css/index.css" rel="stylesheet" />
<div class="wrap">
    <p>
        <span>可爱的书友们，由于微信升级，</span><br>
        <span>如充值时提示“不允许跨号支付”</span>
    </p>
    <p>请按照如下操作方式进行充值哦</p>
    <div class="step">
        <p>第一步：点击充值页面右上方“...”按钮</p>
        <div class="step_img">
            <img src="~/Content/wx/css/1.png" />
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="step">
        <p>第二步：点击“在聊天中置顶”按钮</p>
        <div class="step_img">
            <img src="~/Content/wx/css/2.png" />
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
        <p>第三部：回到微信首页点击聊天最顶部的链接，即可继续完成充值</p>
        <div class="step_img">
            <img src="~/Content/wx/css/3.png" />
        </div>
    </div>
    <p>给大家带来的不便我们深表歉意。</p>
</div>
<a class="btn" href="@("/order/recharge".GetChannelRouteUrl(channelId))">返回</a>

